text: James Warnock is an electrical engineer at the IBM Thomas J. Watson Research Corporation in Yorktown Heights, New York. He was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2012 for his contributions to the circuit design of high-performance microprocessors. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
